 precise individual measurements at the\nZ0 pole (to about +/- 0.00025). This experiment will be complementary to\nQ^p_weak in terms of sensitivity to New Physics.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 5 Feb 2008 18:02:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-13"}
